Moving vertically in a file
@vim

• <Ctrl-e> Scroll downwards
• <Ctrl-y> Scroll upwards
• { and }  Paragraphs backward/forward
• zz       Center screen in middle of cursor
• zt       Center screen with cursor at top
• zb       Center screen with cursor at bottom
• M        Place cursor at middle of screen
• H        Place cursor at top of screen
• L        Place cursor at bottom of screen
